Kingo kagobata ng'alaaletap Job ak choronokyik, konyoonji `Kamuktaindet ineendet ak koteebsee eng' tuguuk che chaang'. Kiyae nooto asi koneetee Job agobo etunatennyi, utotyennyi ne ineegei ak koboorchi kole inee ko ne po kamuktaet tugul ak ko punu kaberuret tugul.

Iboorwech kitabuuni kole kabwaatutik ak ortinwekap Kamuktaindet ko eechen ak ko torooreen ak ma imuuchi chii kosyach anan ko kuiyo. Tetei inee tuguuk ak kowendi kotwoisye ama teebe chii.

